data.description: Country living but close to town, shopping, schools and hospital, this 4 bedroom 2 bath, split floor plan home has been meticulously renovated to include a new primary suite with en suite, complete with ceramic tile flooring.  The gorgeous, open kitchen boasts brand new stainless steel appliances and granite counter tops. Flooring is new LVP.  Outside you will find a fenced, large well manicured front and back yard.  The back deck faces the shop/office (that could be turned into an ADU), above ground pool and a stand alone building that could be used as just about anything.This home offers two high producing wells housed in separate well houses, fruit trees and two types of grapes.The covered RV parking provides 30 amp service and easy turn around. This home and property has so much to offer, too much to list here! The possibilities are endless. Please call today for a list of ALL the upgrades and add ons and to make your easy to show appt.  Act quick.  This gem will not last long.
